191
00:09:18,390 --> 00:09:19,230
Zaozao,

192
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,870
is Su Tangli

193
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:23,550
the Jianglin maiden

194
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,390
Buddy was engaged to?

195
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:26,790
You don't know either?

196
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:36,200
Though they were childhood sweethearts,

197
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:38,960
from what I know,

198
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,320
Lady Su

199
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:42,510
isn't the same person anymore.

200
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,440
But

201
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:47,960
Buddy still cherishes old feelings

202
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:50,480
and can't forget her.

203
00:09:59,260 --> 00:10:00,390
I went to the academy seeking you.

204
00:10:00,730 --> 00:10:02,030
The headmaster said you had left.

205
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,360
Where did you go?

206
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,510
To clear my father's name,

207
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:07,550
I can't remain confined at the academy.

208
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:10,960
I'm now at Prince Yu Residence.

209
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:14,910
Why Prince Yu?

210
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,270
Prince Rui follows laws strictly.

211
00:10:20,750 --> 00:10:22,550
Does that guarantee justice?

212
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:26,670
When my father was framed
and the evidence seemed irrefutable,

213
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:28,720
the law made a conviction inevitable.

214
00:10:30,550 --> 00:10:32,270
Could Prince Rui help then?

215
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,600
Prince Yu's different.

216
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:38,720
He achieves his goals by any means.

217
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,720
Since both use others,

218
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:44,670
