219
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:47,390
One that can slaughter my foes.

220
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:50,720
Prince Rui was indeed powerless then.

221
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,790
But now he's pushing for a retrial.

222
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,390
He appointed the Minister
of Supreme Court

223
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,750
and recruited me

224
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:57,840
for this purpose.

225
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,480
Besides, he promised

226
00:11:00,150 --> 00:11:00,990
to protect you.

227
00:11:01,630 --> 00:11:03,200
Currently, you're in high demand.

228
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:04,750
To attract talent,

229
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:06,360
he must cater to your interests.

230
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,680
For those in power,

231
00:11:07,910 --> 00:11:09,630
