Prince Rui faces court criticism.

235
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,120
He's not the ideal patronage.

236
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:21,670
Why not join Prince Yu?

237
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:24,550
If you can use his power and methods,

238
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,670
you can definitely become powerful

239
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,150
and boost your ambitions.

240
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:29,840
I only know Prince Yu clings to old ways

241
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:31,270
and protects established powers.

242
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:33,750
He conflicts with my goals.

243
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,320
Moreover, have you considered

244
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:37,600
