245
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:40,080
was Prince Yu's faction's doing?

246
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,750
Naturally, I suspected it.

247
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:44,870
If that's the case,

248
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:47,150
being near Prince Yu

249
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:49,240
can aid my investigation.

250
00:11:50,670 --> 00:11:51,550
Don't worry.

251
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,080
Those who harmed my father,

252
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,360
even if it's Prince Yu,

253
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,200
will face my blade.

254
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:58,800
Tangli,

255
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:01,390
I vowed to clear your father's name.

256
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:03,550
Why are you risking yourself?

257
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:05,320
Can your dangerous path now

258
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,630
truly honor his memory?

259
00:12:08,290 --> 00:12:09,270
You don't have to persuade me.

260
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,120
You have your way.

261
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,080
I have mine.

262
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:14,870
If you won't join me with Prince Yu,

263
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,200
